                <h3>Roth Conversions Before 65</h3>
                <p>Strategically convert traditional IRA funds to Roth before Medicare enrollment when income may be lower.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="service-tag">Strategy 3</div>
                <h3>Qualified Charitable Distributions</h3>
                <p>QCDs from your IRA directly to charity satisfy RMDs without increasing your MAGI for IRMAA purposes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="service-tag">Strategy 4</div>
                <h3>Municipal Bond Income</h3>
                <p>While muni bond interest is tax-free, it still counts toward MAGI. We help balance tax-free income with IRMAA thresholds.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
